name: I Flew WestJet's INAUGURAL Flight to Tokyo!
description:
Back in December last year, WestJet announced their first ever destination in Asia - Tokyo, Japan! Predictably, I kinda booked myself a ticket on that inaugural flight the same day.

The flight took place earlier this week, and it was certainly a memorable one for a few different reasons!
